              <h4 style={{ fontSize: 13, color: "#818cf8", margin: "0 0 10px", fontWeight: 700 }}>Lagging Indicators (Weeks 4‚Äì6+)</h4>
              <ul style={{ fontSize: 13, color: "#cbd5e1", margin: 0, paddingLeft: 16, lineHeight: 1.8 }}>
